PESHAWAR, Apr 10 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan arrived on a day-long visit to Peshawar on Friday where he was received by Governor Khyber Pakthunkhwa Shah Farman and Chief Minister Mahmood Khan.
The Prime Minister was accompanied by Federal Minister Shahryar Afridi and Special Assistant to the Prime Minister on Social Protection and Poverty Alleviation, Dr. Sania Nishtar.
